miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic000833_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"Photo J. Prag, Aut. Assessorato Beni Culturali Regione Siciliana n.10681 del 06/05/2014\" src=\"ISic000833_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic000833.jpg\"><img title=\"Photo J. Prag, Aut. Assessorato Beni Culturali Regione Siciliana n.10681 del 06/05/2014\" src=\"ISic000833-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span>  <span>Text after Kaibel in IG 14.13, but preliminarily compared to Orsi's apograph and checked against the stone</span>  </span>; </li><li><span class=\"line 6\">line.6: <span>Kaibel, Manganaro, Aneziri, LeGuen: -]ΥΕΡΓΕΤΗΝ</span>  </span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2> translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\">  </p><p>  </p></div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>See the related CAP entry: <a href=\" http://ancientassociations.ku.dk/assoc/70\" target=\"_blank\">http://ancientassociations.ku.dk/assoc/70</a>  </p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> 53.1033ter <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796</a>  </li><li> 50.1025 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796</a>  </li><li> Orsi NSA 1889 384 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392</a>  </li><li> Kaibel 1890 <a href=\"https://clio.columbia.edu/catalog/6873760\" target=\"_blank\">13</a>  <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072</a>  </li><li> Kaibel 1890 685 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072</a>  </li><li> Rizzo 1923 125 no.1 fig.57 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001638\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001638</a>  </li><li> Manganaro 1963 58-59 ph <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001850\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001850</a>  </li><li> Le Guen 2001 320 no.74 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001883\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001883</a>  </li><li> Aneziri 2003 401 F3 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000641\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000641</a>  </li><li> Orsi 2018 Tacc. 1, p. 40 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002617\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002617</a>  </li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> <p>The letters are notably less regular than <a href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic000832\" target=\"_blank\">ISic000832</a>. Omicron is full; omega is closed; mu has splayed hastae and extended upper strokes; sigma has parallel top and bottom strokes; psi has short upward angled arms; epsilon has nearly equal length bars</p> <p> Types list: <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Α-type1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Α type1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Α-type1.3.html\" target=\"_blank\">Α type1.3</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ε-type2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ε type2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ε-type2.1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ε type2.1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Λ-type2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Λ type2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Μ-type2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Μ type2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/